  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is discussed throughout the assessment narrative; however, not all validation results carry formal UQ artifact links — several results characterize uncertainty in prose only. Full 13-factor assessment with all required fields populated. Decision: Accepted.",
